
;魔力貯蔵器の上限を書き換え
@MAGIC_STORAGE

IF ITEM:魔改造魔力貯蔵器
	IF FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 < MAGIC_TANK_MAD_CAPACITY
		FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 = MAGIC_TANK_MAD_CAPACITY
		PRINTFORMW Mana storage capacity has been increased to %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_MAD_CAPACITY)%MP.
	ENDIF
ELSEIF ITEM:大容量魔力貯蔵器
	IF FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 < MAGIC_TANK_LARGE_CAPACITY
		FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 = MAGIC_TANK_LARGE_CAPACITY
		PRINTFORMW Mana storage capacity has been increased to %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_LARGE_CAPACITY)%MP.
	ENDIF
ELSEIF ITEM:業務用魔力貯蔵器
	IF FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 < MAGIC_TANK_BUSINESSUSE
		FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 = MAGIC_TANK_BUSINESSUSE
		PRINTFORMW Mana storage capacity has been increased to %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_BUSINESSUSE)%MP.
	ENDIF
ELSEIF ITEM:家庭用魔力貯蔵器
	IF FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 < MAGIC_TANK_HOMEUSE
		FLAG:貯蔵魔力上限値 = MAGIC_TANK_HOMEUSE
		PRINTFORMW Mana storage capacity has been increased to%VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_HOMEUSE)%MP.
	ENDIF
ENDIF


